:name:
Praestiga III

:coretxt:
Any illusion you create lasts exactly as long as you want.
In addition, you can create illusionary people in your presence.
These cannot harm or hinder anyone who does not believe they exist.
However, not believing in something that is real can have dire consequences.

:cost:
2 Instinct

